cgcloud__Custom_Calendar__c.name: cgcloud__Custom_Calendar__c
cgcloud__Custom_Calendar__c.description: This object stores the attributes of the custom calendar.

LastReferencedDate.description: The most recent date on which a user referenced this record.

LastViewedDate.description: Most recent date on which a user viewed this record.

cgcloud__Activated_By_Id__c.description: Reference to the user who activated the custom calendar.

cgcloud__Activated_Time__c.description: Stores the timestamp when the custom calendar is activated.

cgcloud__Active__c.description: Reference to the custom calendar that's activated for the sales org.

cgcloud__Description__c.description: Description based on the user-specified language.

cgcloud__ExternalId__c.description: Stores the unique case-sensitive external ID.

cgcloud__Last_Extended_By_Id__c.description: Reference to the user who extended the custom calendar.

cgcloud__Last_Extended_Time__c.description: Stores the timestamp when the custom calendar was extended.

cgcloud__Sales_Org__c.description: Describes the sales organization to which the custom calendar belongs.
